    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">NEW Mechanism-Editor - and the Assembly-Tree</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:240px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-AT-AddMechanism.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Assembly-Tree and the new Mechanism-Editor</title><caption><![CDATA[Assembly-Tree and the new Mechanism-Editor]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">The hierarchy of the new elements </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="VariableName">Front-View</text> of the <text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="color:#ff0000;">new</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text>:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="4" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism2</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> - is a child to </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane4</text><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Element">BasePart2</text> &#160;- is a child to <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism2</text><text styleclass="Element">.</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">The <text styleclass="Interface">XY-Plane</text> of <text styleclass="Element">Plane4, Mechanism2,</text> and <text styleclass="Element">Base-Part2</text> are coplanar and coincident.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
